*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.lof
*.lot
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex.gz
*.synctex(busy)

# === Bibliography / indexing ===
*.bbl
*.blg
*.idx
*.ilg
*.ind

